data.description: This single-story spacious home is in a quiet neighborhood on a lovely street ending with a cul-de-sac. This beautiful home has large living room (your large screen TV will look great over the fireplace and seller is leaving you the bracket), wood laminate floors, large closets w/built-in storage racks, formal dining which opens to living/kitchen, great kitchen with island and kitchenette area also open to living, gas fireplace, floored attic storage and storage shed (or she shed) out back with electric, sprinkler system. Great split plan. Nice covered patio! Great Schools! Close to restaurants and shopping. Community Pool, Clubhouse, Tennis Courts, Volleyball and park.  Must see to appreciate!
